      "text": "19. Un tee Uhdeni wairojahs\npahr leeku fohti wirs Semmes /\nun tappe pahrxeinti wiſſi augſti\nKalni/wiffur appakſch Debbesin."
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "20. Peezpadeſmits Ohleſchu\nAugſtumi wairojahs tee Uhdeni/\nuu tee Kalni tappe pahrxeinti."
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "21. Tad iſlaide to Dshwibu\nwiſſa Meefa / kas wirs Semmes\neustahs / no Putneem / un no\nLohpeem/ un no wiſſadeem Tahr-\npeem/ kas wirs Semmes leen/un\nwiſſi Zilweki."
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "22. Wiſſ kam ta Dwafcha\nweena dshwa BarraNahſis bija/\nno wiſſa/kas Sausuma bija/tas\nnomirre."
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "23. Tad tappe iſdeſdeta wiſſa\nBuhſhana Semmes Wirfu / no\nZilwekeem uſ Lohpeem/ us Tahr-\npeem / un us Putneem appakſch\nDebbes/tomehr Noiſs ween atlik-\nfe/ un kas ar to Schkirsta bija."
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "24. Un tee Uhdeni wairojahs\nwirs Semmes ſimts un peezdeſ-\nmits Deenas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta VIII. Nodalla.\nLas Uhdens eet Masuma : 2. Un kad ta Semme\nfaſikusi : 13. Jsgahje Noiſs no Schkirsta :\n15. Un uppureja Dedsamus. Uppurus : 20\nPar to dabbu wiſſch to ſchehligu Avſohliſcha,\nnu/ ka Deews jo prohjam ve gribb wairs is,\ndeldche wiſſu / kas dshwo/ famehr ta Pajaule\nſahw : 21.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "1. Un Deews atgahdajahs\nNoiſs/ un wiſſo Sweh-\nru/uu wiſſo Lohpu/ kas\nto Schkirsta bija/ un Deews\ndewe Wehju wirs Semmes/ un\ntee Uhdeni norimmahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "2. Un ta Besdtibbina Atwoch-\nun tee Debbes Lohgi tappa ni-\nbahſti/ un tas Leetus no Debbe\ntappa aisturrehts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "3. Un tee Uhdeni atgreeſahs n\nSemmes Wirſu/ ſchurp un tur-\ntezzedami / un tee Uhdeni plak-\npehz ſimts un peezdeſmits De-\nnahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "4. Un tas Schkirſts nolaſdah-\nſeptita Mehneſi/ ſeptita paſdefmi-\nta Mehnes Deena/ us teem Ka-\nneem Abrarat.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "5. Un tee Uhdeni ſkrebje ſchur-\nun turp lihds definitam Mehne-\nſim : definita Mehneſi / pirin-\nMehnes Deena rahdijahs tee Ra-\nno Galli.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "6. Un tas notikke pehz tschetr-\ndeſmits Deenahm / tad atwehr-\nNeiſs ta Schkirſta Lohgu / ko-\nwinsch bij darrijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "7. Un iſlaide weenu Kraukli-\nun tas ſtraidija ſchurp un turp-\nkamehr tee Uhdeni ſafikke no-\nSemmes Wirfu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "8. Pehz to iſlaide winsch Ba-\nlodi no fewim / ka tas fajustu / ar-\nrig tee Uhdeni jaw noskrehuſch-\nno Semmes Wirfu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "9. Bet tas Ballodis ne atrad-\nde fur winska Kahja duſſeht war-\nretu / un atgreeſahs us winsu-\nSchkirsta / jo tee Uhdeni bija pa-\nwiss as Semmes Wirfu/ un winsch-\ntesſeepe ſawu Rohtu / un kampe-\nto / un ecſehwe to pee fewim-\nSchkirsta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "10. Un winsch pagaidija weh-\nſeptinas zittas Deenas / un iſ-\n"
    }
  ],
